# Documentation Index

When you add, remove, rename, or move any file in `docs/`:

1. Update `docs/INDEX.md`: add or remove the entry; fix path if renamed. One-line summary per doc.
2. Update **Last Updated** and **Total Documents**.
3. Keep categories and cross-references alphabetical.

